{"tid":1553914,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"日本山陰地區米子夜晚有咩做??","createTime":"2019-09-08T18:30:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T12:09:11.000Z","uid":314558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"997ebf6618a673174b091cde3a19edfe044b0107","tid":1553914,"uid":314558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T18:30:57.000Z","msg":"本人之前去過山陰<br />\n不過行程飛左米子呢個地方,直接去左境港<br />\n黎緊我會同屋企人再去山陰<br />\n因為想去大山同境港同安來呢三個地方,一日又去唔晒<br />\n咁一定要住米子<br />\n行程其實係:<br />\nDay 3: 倉吉-&gt; 安來-&gt;10:30 足立美術館-&gt; 14:00境港-&gt; <span style=\"color: red;\">18:00米子</span><br />\nDay 4: 米子-&gt; 9:30 大山-&gt;入松江<br />\n問題出左係個米子夜晚到, 好似咩都無<br />\n足立同大山同境港shift唔到 唔會住皆生溫泉<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有無人有介紹?夜晚可以做咩?有咩可以行?</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"b6201f411e52e106cf5bcdbe31b0c57f8a58257a","tid":1553914,"uid":251769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T18:31:26.000Z","msg":"[急!!!]9/9有班中學生等緊你地救！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1553800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1553800</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1168c94a7bf5246adfad3da42ac995ae194a20a2","tid":1553914,"uid":129664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T18:40:31.000Z","msg":"夜晚只得Aeon開到10點，仲要留意入面有啲鋪8、9點就關門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adc4abf5db565efa2c5d482e0485c2ea7b246f3c","tid":1553914,"uid":250118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:03:16.000Z","msg":"睇你幾多月去 冬天好似有鳥取花迴廊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過都唔係開到好夜"},{"pid":"c2989c12be55f7cadd1cc1715fef695d0303a610","tid":1553914,"uid":201374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:49:29.000Z","msg":"去得哩啲山旮旯就唔好預7點後有節目<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f076673c80edee1de1a899771b949c708a58c55","tid":1553914,"uid":256580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci